<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
<head>
	<link href="/static/site.css" rel="stylesheet">
	<title>Display social card url to be used on Twitter or Facebook</title>
<body>
	<h1>Url to be used on Twitter or Facebook</h1>
	
	<p>https://picktwt.herokuapp.com/query?url=<%= query.url %>&image_url=<%= query.image_url %>&title=<%= query.title %>&image_alt=<%= query.image_alt %>&description=<%= query.description %></p>

	<h2>Target</h2>
	<p>It will automatically redirect to <a href="<%= query.url %>"><%= query.url %></a></p>

	<h2>Image</h2>
	<p>It will show the picture:</p>
	<p><img src="<%= query.image_url %>" alt="<%= query.image_alt %>"></img></p>

	<h2>Caption</h2>
	<p>It will have some caption like</p>
	<div class="example">
	<h3><%= query.title %></h3>
	<p><%= query.description %>
	</p>
	</div>

